data.description: This is the home you have been waiting for. Stop paying your landlords mortgage and start investing in your future. Magnolia Lakes is a highly sought after neighborhood in Gateway. Close to shopping, dinning, entertainment. If you need to get away, Southwest Florida International Airport is less than 15 minutes away. (Depending on your driving skills) This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom 3 car garage home is spacious enough to find peace away from family or guests, yet cozy enough to snuggle with said family or guests when the time is right. This home is move in ready, with just your toothbrush, personal belongings, and if you like furniture, you can bring that too!
